  "detailed_description": "\"Dosoland: Snake Man’s Adventure\" is a short and easy-to-play platformer. Explore the environments to uncover secrets, jump on enemies, and dash through obstacles. Your mission? Save Earth from an alien invasion, all while accompanied by a team of quirky and endearing friends you meet along the way.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1500300/extras/412181c9c5897a48dd1c7be4b130cf30.poster.avif?t=1712228702\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1500300/extras/412181c9c5897a48dd1c7be4b130cf30.webm?t=1712228702\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1500300/extras/412181c9c5897a48dd1c7be4b130cf30.mp4?t=1712228702\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Help Snake Man save Earth in this unique platform adventure. Discover a fantastic game world. Fight a variety of enemies. Explore the environment for hidden secrets that help Snake Man become more and more powerful over time. Looking for a challenge? Try a speedrun and set your new personal record with the built-in timer.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1500300/extras/52453031af8a9b58ce83433625d77976.poster.avif?t=1712228702\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1500300/extras/52453031af8a9b58ce83433625d77976.webm?t=1712228702\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1500300/extras/52453031af8a9b58ce83433625d77976.mp4?t=1712228702\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Universe Is Bigger Than You Think.</strong></h2><br>Luckily Snake Man is not alone – on his journey he will meet new friends from Earth, but also from all over the universe. This could be the beginning of quite an unusual team…<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1500300/extras/9cbca370af9bf99059c5307d4df54824.avif?t=1712228702\" width=620 height=220 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "\"Dosoland: Snake Man’s Adventure\" is a short and easy-to-play platformer. Explore the environments to uncover secrets, jump on enemies, and dash through obstacles. Your mission? Save Earth from an alien invasion, all while accompanied by a team of quirky and endearing friends you meet along the way.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1500300/extras/412181c9c5897a48dd1c7be4b130cf30.poster.avif?t=1712228702\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1500300/extras/412181c9c5897a48dd1c7be4b130cf30.webm?t=1712228702\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1500300/extras/412181c9c5897a48dd1c7be4b130cf30.mp4?t=1712228702\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Help Snake Man save Earth in this unique platform adventure. Discover a fantastic game world. Fight a variety of enemies. Explore the environment for hidden secrets that help Snake Man become more and more powerful over time. Looking for a challenge? Try a speedrun and set your new personal record with the built-in timer.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1500300/extras/52453031af8a9b58ce83433625d77976.poster.avif?t=1712228702\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1500300/extras/52453031af8a9b58ce83433625d77976.webm?t=1712228702\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1500300/extras/52453031af8a9b58ce83433625d77976.mp4?t=1712228702\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Universe Is Bigger Than You Think.</strong></h2><br>Luckil